ActCourts Administration Service Act
PrecisConfirm that RAYMOND P. GUENETTE of Ottawa, Ontario, a Deputy Chief Administrator, may continue to act as Chief Administrator of the Courts Administration Service, for the period commencing on June 4, 2005 and terminating on June 3, 2006.
